                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">What I LIKE:
<br />
- I like the flaws of shadowstep. I like that this isn't 100% reliable and you have to use it wisely.
<br />
- I like the 30-minute timer. This is fine with me, although I do think reducing it by 5 minutes for each higher level of Doppleganger is a great idea.
<br />

<br />
What I DISLIKE:
<br />
- That the ability doesn't ditch aggro at all, just acts like a pseudo-rune. I would like to see Doppleganger insty-cast Boggle on the mob as well.
<br />
- That you can pull mobs with doppleganger. This is the single stupidest part of this AA. Even if the ability doesn't boggle the mobs, it should add 0 aggro. Furthermore, I can only assume that we are gaining even more aggro while DG melees. This, too, needs to be fixed somehow. The mob thinks you're dead. That's the whole point.
<br />

<br />
I think DG is one of the best story ideas that SOE came up with in Gates of Discord. I would like to see them improve it by eliminating all aggro transfered to you from Mr. D. and adding a Boggle ability when cast. Lastly, some type of improvement at additional levels would make them useful. If not a reduced reuse timer, perhaps level 2 could prevent aggro transfer and level 3 would add the boggle.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: normal"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=361216" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ariu <span style="font-style: italic">stop destroying my class damnit!</span> Vil''''Aki &lt;Heroes&gt;</a>
