                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/agree pets definitely put you on hate list
<br />

<br />
However, there is something to be said regarding the amount of hate generated.  After enough attempts at Rydda Dar, I'm pretty confident we aren't getting the full hate generated by our pet's damage.  Some of that hate may even be reduced after a charm break.  Rampage adds in another factor (we had pets taking ramp damange on RD with many PCs in range - this seems to be the one exception to the atk PC's first rule).
<br />

<br />
Long story short - if chanters got full hate for pet dps, we'd be getting summoned on raids instead of the mob ping-ponging to a melee or healer when a tank goes down.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="color: darkblue"> 
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=831098" target="_blank" class="postlink">Visionary Nokei Orhaste</a></span>
